---
title: Chicken and Spinach Salad with Cheesy Broiled Zucchini and Tomatoes
description: Broiling veggies rather than roasting saves time, and adding cheese and panko to them adds a bit of pizzazz!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-and-spinach-salad-415948ac.jpg
